These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
City: rome, prague
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, mexican
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the mexican##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to prague is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| City   | prague     | rome   |
| Nationality         | mexican | polish |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, blood-red
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, may
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Color          | aquamarine     | blood-red |
| Birthday   | may | august  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: orange, carrot
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, water-polo
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Food         | carrot | orange    |
| Sport         | cricket         | water-polo        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

