.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-12::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, indie
There 2 different types of food: tomato, lettuce
1. the person eating lettuce is in an even position##4
2. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | writing   | rock-climbing |
| Cigar           | prince | game    |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | indie         |
| Food         | tomato   | lettuce |

